前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/111%2c%e6%98%93%2c17%2c20220217%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,111,易,17,20220217,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"易","JNO":"17","JDATE":"20220217","JTITLE":"竊盜"}